T1  - Does order preferencing matter?1We would like to thank David Easley, Eugene Kandel (the referee), G. William Schwert (the editor), participants at the Dealer Markets Conference at Ohio State University and an anonymous referee for helpful comments. We gratefully acknowledge financial support from the Johnson Graduate School of Management and the National Science Foundation.1
